commentTextItems.html: quicker ball on middle, onto the backfoot to defend but gets beaten and it hits the middle of middle stump, that secures the win for Afghanistan in the first of the five ODI's by a handsome margin of 154 runs

looped outside off, goes for a sweep but misses it
flighted up, comes down and meets it with full face of the bat and gets it high and all the way over long-on for a six

milestones.description: Zadran and Rahmat Shah's 158-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 157 between Zadran and Rahmat Shah
Afghanistan's 154-run win against Zimbabwe is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 138-run win against Ireland
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (5) in ODIs for AFG, going past Asghar Afghan's 5
